---

<section id="start" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); background:#0a0a0b;">
  <div style="max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:84px 32px;" class="section-pad">
    <div
      data-reveal
      class="docs-check-inner"
      style="border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10); border-radius:16px; padding:34px 36px; background:#0d0d0f; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.3fr 1fr; gap:40px; align-items:center;"
    >
      <div>
        <div
          style="font-family:'Geist Mono',monospace; font-size:11.5px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#8b8b8b; margin-bottom:14px;"
        >
          Not ready for a full engagement? Start here · 1–2 weeks
        </div>
        <h3
          style="font-weight:600; font-size:24px; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin:0 0 12px; color:#fafafa;"
        >
          Docs Health Check
        </h3>
        <p style="font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.65; color:#9a9a9a; margin:0;">
          A fast, fixed-price audit of your docs and first-run developer experience. You get a
          prioritized report of gaps, confusing onboarding points, and quick wins — things you can
          act on immediately. Optional add-on: I execute the top fixes at a separate fixed fee,
          scoped after the audit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px;">
        <div
          style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; font-size:14px; padding-bottom:14px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);"
        >
          <span style="color:#8b8b8b;">Timeline</span>
          <span style="color:#ededed;">1–2 weeks</span>
        </div>
        <div
          style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; font-size:14px; padding-bottom:14px; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);"
        >
          <span style="color:#8b8b8b;">Price</span>
          <span style="color:#ededed;">Flat fee</span>
        </div>
        <div
          style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; font-size:14px; padding-bottom:18px;"
        >
          <span style="color:#8b8b8b;">Deliverable</span>
          <span style="color:#ededed;">Prioritized audit report</span>
        </div>
        <a href="#contact" class="docs-cta">Book a Docs Health Check →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
